title: GoPro VR: Diving With a Blue Whale
description:
For the full GoPro Spherical 360 virtual reality experience, view on your mobile device or the Kolor app 

Explore by using your mouse or the ASWD keys to move around!

Freedive with a blue whale off the coast of Mexico with GoPro Creative Director, Brad Schmidt, as he sets out to capture one of a kind footage for the feature film 'Racing Extinction'.

The film will premiere worldwide on Discovery on Dec 2 at 9/8c. 

Shot 100% on the HERO4®
